farside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/04/0</guid><pubDate>Sat, 04 Jul 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>